{"tid":2416770,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣奇幻愛情喜劇 金馬獎最佳劇情長片《消失的情人節》討論區","createTime":"2021-02-21T10:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T09:25:51.000Z","uid":346775,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"228f074fe2641497336955b0e5ee0905c83ac702","tid":2416770,"uid":346775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T10:13:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/147843949_5042639555806329_2478044760620521634_o.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;ccb=3&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=afjfCrPkE1UAX_ag6S5&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=b37c1667af825dd61d2f42b3cb94a711&amp;oe=6057FCE0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F147843949_5042639555806329_2478044760620521634_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26ccb%3D3%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DafjfCrPkE1UAX_ag6S5%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Db37c1667af825dd61d2f42b3cb94a711%26oe%3D6057FCE0&h=b8b139e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第57屆金馬獎最大贏家 獲11項提名 奪5項大獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n包括最佳劇情長片、最佳導演、最佳原著劇本、最佳剪輯、最佳視覺效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n預告：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rGBFr8v_K28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrGBFr8v_K28&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=89ac72a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rGBFr8v_K28</a><br />\n<br />\n在郵局工作的曉淇（李霈瑜 飾）是個超級急性子，她行事俐落、反應敏捷，偏偏愛情卻急不來，活了三十年依然單身。日復日沉悶的工作中，她發現有個慢半拍的寄信男（劉冠廷 飾），不論陰晴也每天到郵局寄一封神秘的信。情人節前夕，憧憬愛情的曉淇終遇上了陽光男搭訕約會，脫單在望。怎料一覺醒來，她期待而久的情人節居然消失了！斷了片的她完全沒有那天的記憶，就連陽光男與「慢世魔王」寄信男也同時失蹤！ 曉淇決意踏上奇幻之程，尋找消失一天的真相，奪回屬於自己的幸福。<br />\n<br />\n幾經波折終於上正場喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 優先場已上，2月25號正式上映"},{"pid":"ecbaca2c96fe6c5cb6c79d2356e21599622e86e9","tid":2416770,"uid":313584,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T10:14:54.000Z","msg":"呢套正嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44540ca8972b37b3f2976100f09c6e332c338e82","tid":2416770,"uid":30294,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"ecbaca2c96fe6c5cb6c79d2356e21599622e86e9","tid":2416770,"uid":313584,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T10:14:54.000Z","msg":"呢套正嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T10:22:24.000Z","msg":"岩睇完 反而覺得好普通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小品喜劇黎講幾好睇 但未到贏哂既lv<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34818a0d46bf5d7b706545f9f84cc5c234d9d7f4","tid":2416770,"uid":151760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T10:29:15.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啱啱睇咗"},{"pid":"05a6760007caae511dcff5406542dee7e1e81221","tid":2416770,"uid":346775,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T10:31:17.000Z","msg":"主題曲MV（由女主角大霈主唱同作詞）：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4mURiGCdmJc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4mURiGCdmJc&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=a3c995ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4mURiGCdmJc</a><br />\n獲提名第57屆金馬獎最佳原創電影歌曲<br />\n<br />\n導演：陳玉勳<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2020-11-21/656/20201121004191.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2020-11-21%2F656%2F20201121004191.jpg&h=f9ddb981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n作品包括《熱帶魚》(1994)、《愛情來了》(1997)、《總舖師》(2013)<br />\n憑本片獲得金馬獎最佳導演獎<br />\n<br />\n主演<br />\n<br />\n李霈瑜（大霈）<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ZVf2zBGEeUaIXB4QExIwSQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTg4OC4wOTg3NjU0MzIwOTg3/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/wKu8lTwevh_u4CYLNlG7qg--~B/aD0xMTI0O3c9ODEwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/ctwant_com_582/07c84650db6c554d1cd731730eb3358f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZVf2zBGEeUaIXB4QExIwSQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTg4OC4wOTg3NjU0MzIwOTg3%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FwKu8lTwevh_u4CYLNlG7qg--~B%2FaD0xMTI0O3c9ODEwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fctwant_com_582%2F07c84650db6c554d1cd731730eb3358f&h=1dbf044b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首度擔任女主角即獲提名金馬獎最佳女主角<br />\n曾於2019年以旅遊節目《水下三十米》獲第54屆金鐘獎生活風格節目主持人獎 <br />\n<br />\n劉冠廷<br />\n<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/amv-prod-elletw.s3.amazonaws.com/new-dossier/liu1.jpg?crop=1xw:0.6666666666666666xh;center,top&amp;resize=480:*\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Famv-prod-elletw.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fnew-dossier%2Fliu1.jpg%3Fcrop%3D1xw%3A0.6666666666666666xh%3Bcenter%2Ctop%26resize%3D480%3A%2A&h=f5e3e0ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以電視劇《植劇場－花甲男孩轉大人》拿下第53屆金鐘獎戲劇節目男配角獎，以及電影《陽光普照》奪得第56屆金馬獎最佳男配角獎<br />\n近年許多台灣電影都能看到他的蹤影，包括《無聲》、《同學麥娜絲》等等<br />\n憑本片提名金馬獎最佳男主角<br />\n<br />\n黑嘉嘉(Joanne Missingham)<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/www-cw-com-tw/ckeditor/201911/ckeditor-5dc0e857e8180.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Fwww-cw-com-tw%2Fckeditor%2F201911%2Fckeditor-5dc0e857e8180.jpg&h=af676a80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n臺灣女子職業圍棋選手，圍棋職業七段，世界圍棋女子大賽亞軍<br />\n近年開始踏入演藝圈<br />\n<br />\n周群達(Ducan)<br />\n<img src=\"https://movies.yahoo.com.tw/i/o/production/names/August2020/rb3FNfb599EHW3qtD5aP-547x366.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmovies.yahoo.com.tw%2Fi%2Fo%2Fproduction%2Fnames%2FAugust2020%2Frb3FNfb599EHW3qtD5aP-547x366.jpg&h=daac29d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n活躍在港、台的男演員，前香港滑浪風帆隊的代表，香港奧運滑浪風帆金牌得主李麗珊的表弟。<br />\n<br />\n香港亞洲電影節 映後談重溫<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/137413099621763/videos/756892588505112\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F137413099621763%2Fvideos%2F756892588505112&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=fef9f2ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/137413099621763/videos/756892588505112</a>"},{"pid":"f584d77f7653b6d5df3128e310ffa6aded2a2f0b","tid":2416770,"uid":346775,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T10:32:55.000Z","msg":"打錯 係Duncan先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1a20dd27a016e253fd2ce8f9624261f1fdc77e","tid":2416770,"uid":30294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"05a6760007caae511dcff5406542dee7e1e81221","tid":2416770,"uid":346775,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T10:31:17.000Z","msg":"主題曲MV（由女主角大霈主唱同作詞）：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4mURiGCdmJc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4mURiGCdmJc&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=a3c995ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4mURiGCdmJc</a><br />\n獲提名第57屆金馬獎最佳原創電影歌曲<br />\n<br />\n導演：陳玉勳<br />\n<img src=\"